imdb.plot outline: COUNTERFIT gets what he wants, when he wants - or so he thinks. Without any fear in life, Counterfit lives life moment by moment - and based on his lifestyle - any given moment could be his last. Counterfit's confidence comes from not giving a damn about anything or anyone, and he's only loyal to himself and his beliefs (which he believes in nothing). If there's a way to "come up" he will find it, exploit it, and ruin it for everyone else.
